    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，知识库作为子图。PLC逻辑和控制器之间的关系是？是单向的数据流吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Knowledge_Base",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，PLC逻辑先被分块处理，然后流向控制器。标注为\"1a. Chunk & Process\"。同时知识库整体还要生成嵌入向量，指向一个独立的数据库节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：知识库子图内部是D到C的1a流程，子图外部有1b指向DB。这个DB就是向量数据库对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Knowledge_Base",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，DB存储所有嵌入。接下来需要MQTT Broker作为查询入口，它接收工业现场的实时查询。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加MQTT Broker节点Q。它下一步应该做什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Q要把查询生成嵌入，流向另一个PLC逻辑节点E，然后E用向量相似度搜索去查DB。这是2a和2b两步。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
