      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "这里E和D都是PLC_Logic，但功能不同？D在知识库里，E在外面做查询处理？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完全正确。D是静态知识，E是动态查询侧。DB检索后要把相关块送到CTX上下文节点，标注3。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
