    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，CTX代表上下文组装模块，复用MQTT Broker类型。现在需要把原始查询Q和上下文CTX合并，都流向控制器P。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
