      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，P把组合好的提示发给LLM节点，标注5。LLM生成响应到R节点，标注6。LLM和R都是MQTT Broker类型。",
      "elements_involved": [
